git-fsck - Git Filesystem Check

USAGE:
    git-fsck [--git-user=USER]

DESCRIPTION:
    Perform git fsck on mirrors as administrator.

OPTIONS:
    --git-user=USER
        Git user to run fsck as (conf_git_git_user)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-git-git-user=USER
        Default git user for fsck operations

NOTE:
    Run this command in the root directory where git repositories are kept.

EXAMPLES:
    git-fsck
    git-fsck --git-user=gitadmin